and bloody offering.

31
00:02:07.878 --> 00:02:11.131
May they peer inside
our mortal hearts
and find the truth.

32
00:02:13.050 --> 00:02:15.260
May the Warrior grant victory
to the innocent...

33
00:02:16.470 --> 00:02:18.847
