148
00:10:08.733 --> 00:10:10.777
Hey. don't lose
your nerve now.

149
00:10:12.070 --> 00:10:13.279
The shit part's done.

150
00:10:14.405 --> 00:10:16.032
I know.

151
00:10:16.074 --> 00:10:18.201
