into all kinds of adventures.

152
00:10:18.243 --> 00:10:20.745
-Don't you want that?
-I do.

153
00:10:20.787 --> 00:10:21.913
I just...

154
00:10:24.165 --> 00:10:25.166
What?

155
00:10:27.752 --> 00:10:29.921
