the best there is?

161
00:10:44.102 --> 00:10:45.687
That would be quite sad.

162
00:10:50.525 --> 00:10:54.696
And... what if my mother
comes back for me?

163
00:10:57.991 --> 00:11:00.660
I'm not stupid.
I know she's dead.

164
00:11:01.661 --> 00:11:04.080
But what if she's just
trying to get away

165
00:11:04.122 --> 00:11:06.916
