220
00:14:47.678 --> 00:14:50.056
Little gutter rats
don't have silver.

221
00:14:50.098 --> 00:14:51.307
Only little thieves.

222
00:14:51.349 --> 00:14:53.893
We didn't thieve nothing.
We earned that.

223
00:14:53.935 --> 00:14:56.396
Stealing from dead nobles
