-Oh. you old fool.
-Sorry. I'm sorry.

264
00:18:50.796 --> 00:18:52.798
[groaning]

265
00:18:55.593 --> 00:18:58.596
[♪ soft music playing]

266
00:19:08.481 --> 00:19:12.109
Hey. boys.
Did you miss me? Yeah.

267
00:19:13.903 --> 00:19:15.946
-[crickets chirping]
-[fire crackling]

268
00:19:33.172 --> 00:19:35.174
