Wine. Not oil.

384
00:32:23.066 --> 00:32:24.860
Oil will kill him.

385
00:32:24.901 --> 00:32:27.737
I'll send Maester Yormwell
to have a look at him

386
00:32:27.779 --> 00:32:29.489
when he's done
tending to my brother.

387
00:32:32.242 --> 00:32:33.910
Your Grace.
[grunting]

388
00:32:35.245 --> 00:32:36.746
I am your man.

389
