Please. Your man.

390
00:32:42.836 --> 00:32:44.754
I need good men.
Ser Duncan.

391
00:32:46.923 --> 00:32:48.175
The realm.

392
00:32:49.092 --> 00:32:52.137
[Dunk groaning]

393
00:32:53.305 --> 00:32:54.764
