it's crushed down the back.
Your Grace.

403
00:33:22.959 --> 00:33:24.252
It's smashed
into the gorget.

404
00:33:24.294 --> 00:33:25.879
My brother's mace.
most like.

405
00:33:27.214 --> 00:33:29.049
